				<wikidot:authorName>Buttfranklin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2721810</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm in a similar position to TheMightyMcB. This <em>almost</em> lands for me, but not quite, and I'm not exactly sure why. I think there are too many gaps in the narrative and characters – I don't know what Analiese thinks of these happenings, for instance. Perhaps also because it's slightly too obvious a vehicle for creepypasta – technically, all of this could have been done by some weird-looking non-anomalous guy, so it seems slightly strange that the Foundation is keeping tabs on it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
