					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13582786#post-4729404</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13582786/scp-5622#post-4729404</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 25 Jul 2020 19:16:40 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheMightyMcB</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4483018</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This comes close to securing my upvote but just barely misses the mark. The notes are creepy as shit, but pretty much the entire rest of the article is lacking. The containment procedures and description do very little to hook me as the reader and the ending feels almost too tame for a monster that murdered a guy under the porch earlier in the story. Just moving to stalk this poor girl in prison and bust her out almost lets down the threat issued earlier. I was basically all geared up for a video/audio feed of their breakout and was admittedly disappointed when we didn't get that at all. -1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
